---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const chapters = [
  {
    id: 'ch1', num: 1, status: 'done',
    title: 'Introduction',
    titleZh: '引言',
    pages: 'p1-18',
    blogUrl: '/blog/2026-03-16-box-ch1-introduction/',
    sections: [
      { id: '1.1', title: '五大实际问题', note: String.raw`Box 从五个实际问题出发，每个对应一类数学模型：\n\n①时间序列预测(Forecasting)：已知 $z_t, z_{t-1}, \ldots$，预测 $z_{t+l}$，最小化 MSE $E[(z_{t+l}-\hat{z}_t(l))^2]$。需要概率置信限(50%, 95%)。\n\n②转换函数估计(Transfer Function)：输入 $X_t$ 和输出 $Y_t$ 的动态关系 $Y_t = \sum v_j X_{t-j}$。化学炉例子：空气速率→CO₂浓度。难点是噪声掩盖真实关系。\n\n③干扰分析(Intervention Analysis)：用 0/1 指示变量量化外部事件（政策变化、罢工等）对序列的影响。Box & Tiao (1975) 经典论文。\n\n④多元时间序列：$k$ 个相关序列 $\mathbf{Z}_t = (z_{1t}, \ldots, z_{kt})'$ 的联合建模。目的：①理解动态关系 ②利用相关信息提高预测精度。\n\n⑤离散控制系统：SPC(统计过程控制，Shewhart 图) vs EPC(工程过程控制，反馈/前馈)。预测和控制紧密相连——最小 MSE 预测 → 最小 MSE 控制。` },
      { id: '1.2', title: '随机与确定性动态数学模型', note: String.raw`核心数学框架：\n\n【线性滤波模型】$z_t = \mu + \psi(B)a_t$，白噪声 $a_t$ 经过线性滤波器。$\psi(B) = 1 + \psi_1 B + \psi_2 B^2 + \cdots$\n\n【AR(p)】$\phi(B)\tilde{z}_t = a_t$，$\phi(B) = 1 - \phi_1 B - \cdots - \phi_p B^p$\n平稳条件：$\phi(B)=0$ 的根在单位圆外。AR 是线性滤波的特例：$\psi(B) = \phi^{-1}(B)$。\n\n【MA(q)】$\tilde{z}_t = \theta(B)a_t$，$\theta(B) = 1 - \theta_1 B - \cdots - \theta_q B^q$\n\n【ARMA(p,q)】$\phi(B)\tilde{z}_t = \theta(B)a_t$\n\n【ARIMA(p,d,q)】差分 $d$ 次使非平稳变平稳：$\phi(B)\nabla^d z_t = \theta(B)a_t$\n"Integrated" = 平稳 ARMA 经 $d$ 次求和得到非平稳过程。\n\n【转换函数模型(带噪声)】$Y_t = v(B)X_t + \psi(B)a_t$\n\n【控制方程】$x_t = \zeta_1 x_{t-1} + \cdots + \chi_0 \varepsilon_t + \chi_1 \varepsilon_{t-1} + \cdots$` },
      { id: '1.3', title: '模型构建基本思想', note: String.raw`【简约原则(Parsimony)】用尽可能少的参数获取充分表示。Box 举例：2 参数模型 $(1-\delta B)Y_t = \omega_0 X_t$ 足够时，不要用 $s+1$ 参数的多项式拟合。\n\n【迭代三步法(Box-Jenkins 方法论)】\n1. 识别(Identification)：用 ACF/PACF 确定模型结构 $(p, d, q)$\n2. 估计(Estimation)：MLE 或 最小二乘法估计参数\n3. 诊断检验(Diagnostic Checking)：残差分析\n\n不合格就回到第 1 步循环。至少需要 50 个观测值，最好 100+。` },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch2', num: 2, status: 'done',
    title: 'Autocorrelation Function and Spectrum of Stationary Processes',
    titleZh: '平稳过程的自相关函数与谱',
    pages: 'p21-46',
    blogUrl: '/blog/2026-03-16-box-ch2-acf-spectrum/',
    sections: [
      { id: '2.1.1-2', title: '时间序列、随机过程与平稳性', note: String.raw`离散时间序列 $z_1, z_2, \ldots, z_N$ 是随机过程的一次实现(sample realization)。\n\n严格平稳：任意 $m$ 个时点的联合分布只依赖时间差。\n弱平稳（二阶）：均值常数 $\mu = E[z_t]$，自协方差只依赖滞后 $\gamma_k = \text{cov}[z_t, z_{t+k}]$。\n\n自相关系数 $\rho_k = \gamma_k / \gamma_0$，$\rho_0 = 1$，$\rho_k = \rho_{-k}$。\n\n高斯过程：弱平稳 → 严格平稳（正态分布由一二阶矩完全决定）。\n白噪声：$\gamma_k = \sigma_a^2$ ($k=0$)，$\gamma_k = 0$ ($k \neq 0$)。` },
      { id: '2.1.3', title: '正定性与自协方差矩阵', note: String.raw`$n$ 个连续观测的协方差矩阵是 Toeplitz 矩阵（对角线相同），必须正定。\n\n正定性约束 $\rho_k$ 的取值范围：\n- $n=2$：$|\rho_1| < 1$\n- $n=3$：$-1 < (\rho_2 - \rho_1^2)/(1-\rho_1^2) < 1$\n\n线性运算保平稳：$y_t = \sum \psi_i z_{t-i}$（$\sum|\psi_i|<\infty$）也平稳。这是 ARMA 合法性的基础。\n\n差分 $\nabla^d z_t$ 也平稳——Ch4 非平稳模型的关键前提。` },
      { id: '2.1.5-6', title: 'ACF 估计与 Bartlett 标准误差', note: String.raw`样本 ACF：$r_k = c_k / c_0$，$c_k = \frac{1}{N}\sum_{t=1}^{N-k}(z_t - \bar{z})(z_{t+k} - \bar{z})$\n\n用 $1/N$ 而非 $1/(N-k)$ 作分母——保证估计矩阵半正定。\n\nBartlett 大滞后近似：若 $\rho_v = 0$ ($v > q$)，则 $\text{var}[r_k] \approx \frac{1}{N}(1 + 2\sum_{v=1}^{q} \rho_v^2)$ ($k > q$)\n\n白噪声：$\text{se}[r_k] \approx 1/\sqrt{N}$ → ACF 图上的 $\pm 2/\sqrt{N}$ 显著性带。\n\n重要警告：相邻 $r_k$ 可能高度相关，不能只看单个值。` },
      { id: '2.2', title: '谱性质', note: String.raw`周期图：$I(f_i) = \frac{N}{2}(a_i^2 + b_i^2)$，方差分解到各频率。\n\n样本谱与 ACF 的傅里叶变换关系：$I(f) = 2(c_0 + 2\sum c_k \cos 2\pi fk)$\n\n理论功率谱：$p(f) = 2(\gamma_0 + 2\sum \gamma_k \cos 2\pi fk)$\n\n谱密度：$g(f) = p(f)/\sigma_z^2$，$\int_0^{1/2} g(f)df = 1$\n\n核心定理：$\gamma_k$ 正定 $\Leftrightarrow$ $p(f) \geq 0$ （Herglotz 定理）\n\n样本谱剧烈波动（$\chi^2(2)$ 方差不随 $N$ 减小）→ 需要平滑估计（lag window / spectral window）。\n\n两个 MA(1) 例子：正系数→低频主导（光滑），负系数→高频主导（锯齿）。` },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch3', num: 3, status: 'done',
    title: 'Linear Stationary Models',
    titleZh: '线性平稳模型',
    pages: 'p47-91',
    blogUrl: '/blog/2026-03-16-box-ch3-linear-stationary-models/',
    sections: [
      { id: '3.1', title: '一般线性过程与 Wold 分解', note: String.raw`Wold 分解定理：任何零均值纯非确定性平稳过程都可表示为 $\tilde{z}_t = \sum \psi_j a_{t-j}$。\n\nψ 权重（MA 表示）↔ π 权重（AR 表示）：$\psi(B)\pi(B) = 1$\n\n自协方差生成函数：$\gamma(B) = \sigma_a^2 \psi(B)\psi(B^{-1})$\n\n谱 = 白噪声谱 × 滤波器增益²：$p(f) = 2\sigma_a^2|\psi(e^{-i2\pi f})|^2$\n\n平稳条件：$\psi(B)$ 在 $|B| \leq 1$ 收敛\n可逆条件：$\pi(B)$ 在 $|B| \leq 1$ 收敛` },
      { id: '3.2', title: 'AR(p) 自回归过程', note: String.raw`$\phi(B)\tilde{z}_t = a_t$，平稳条件：$\phi(B)=0$ 根在单位圆外\n\nACF 差分方程：$\rho_k = \phi_1\rho_{k-1} + \cdots + \phi_p\rho_{k-p}$\n通解：衰减指数 + 阻尼正弦波\n\nYule-Walker 方程：$\mathbf{P}_p\boldsymbol{\phi} = \boldsymbol{\rho}_p$（线性，可直接求解）\n\nPACF 关键性质：AR(p) 的 PACF 在 lag p 后截断为零\n\nAR(1)：$\rho_k = \phi_1^k$，马尔可夫过程\nAR(2)：复数根时有伪周期行为，$D = \sqrt{-\phi_2}$，$f_0 = \cos^{-1}(\phi_1/2\sqrt{-\phi_2})/(2\pi)$` },
      { id: '3.3', title: 'MA(q) 移动平均过程', note: String.raw`$\tilde{z}_t = \theta(B)a_t$，恒平稳，可逆条件：$\theta(B)=0$ 根在圆外\n\nACF 关键性质：MA(q) 的 ACF 在 lag q 后截断为零\n\nMA(1)：$\rho_1 = -\theta_1/(1+\theta_1^2)$，$|\rho_1| \leq 0.5$\n给定 $\rho_1$ 有两个解，取可逆解 $|\theta_1| < 1$\n\nAR↔MA 对偶：ACF截断→MA，PACF截断→AR，谱互为倒数` },
      { id: '3.4', title: 'ARMA(p,q) 混合过程', note: String.raw`$\phi(B)\tilde{z}_t = \theta(B)a_t$\n\n平稳 + 可逆条件：$\phi(B)=0$ 和 $\theta(B)=0$ 的根都在圆外\n\nACF：前 $q-p+1$ 个受 $\theta$ 直接影响，之后按差分方程 $\phi(B)\rho_k = 0$ 衰减\nPACF：前 $p-q+1$ 个受 $\phi$ 影响，之后按 MA 型衰减\n\nARMA(1,1)：$\rho_k = \phi_1\rho_{k-1}$ ($k \geq 2$)，从 $\rho_1$ 开始指数衰减\n$\psi_j = (\phi_1-\theta_1)\phi_1^{j-1}$ ($j \geq 1$)` },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch4', num: 4, status: 'done',
    title: 'Linear Nonstationary Models',
    titleZh: '线性非平稳模型',
    pages: 'p93-157',
    blogUrl: '/blog/2026-03-16-box-ch4-arima/',
    sections: [
      { id: '4.1', title: 'ARIMA 过程的定义', note: String.raw`ARIMA(p,d,q)：$\phi(B)\nabla^d z_t = \theta_0 + \theta(B)a_t$\n\n非平稳的三种情况：\n- 根在圆外：平稳（ARMA）\n- 根在圆内：爆炸性（排除）\n- 根在圆上（=1）：齐次非平稳（ARIMA）\n\n$d=1$：水平漂移（最常见），$d=2$：趋势漂移\n$\theta_0 \neq 0$ 引入确定性趋势\n\n实践中 $p, d, q$ 很少 > 2` },
      { id: '4.2', title: '三种显式形式', note: String.raw`①差分方程形式：$z_t = \varphi_1 z_{t-1} + \cdots + a_t - \theta_1 a_{t-1} - \cdots$（计算预测）\n②随机冲击形式：$z_t = \psi(B)a_t$（计算预测误差方差）\n③反转形式：$z_t = \pi_1 z_{t-1} + \cdots + a_t$（EWMA 等价形式）\n\nψ 权重递推：$\varphi(B)\psi(B) = \theta(B)$` },
      { id: '4.3', title: 'IMA 过程与指数平滑', note: String.raw`IMA(0,1,1)：$\nabla z_t = (1-\theta_1 B)a_t$\n反转形式 = EWMA（指数加权移动平均），权重 $(1-\theta_1)\theta_1^j$\n\nIMA(0,2,2)：最优预测沿直线（Holt 双参数指数平滑）\n\nBox 证明：Holt/Brown/Winters 的经验方法是特定 IMA 过程的最优预测——统计基础！` },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch5', num: 5, status: 'pending',
    title: 'Forecasting',
    titleZh: '预测',
    pages: 'p137-192',
    sections: [],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch6', num: 6, status: 'pending',
    title: 'Model Identification',
    titleZh: '模型识别',
    pages: 'p195-239',
    sections: [],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch7', num: 7, status: 'pending',
    title: 'Model Estimation',
    titleZh: '模型估计',
    pages: 'p241-327',
    sections: [],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch8', num: 8, status: 'pending',
    title: 'Model Diagnostic Checking',
    titleZh: '模型诊断检验',
    pages: 'p329-373',
    sections: [],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch9', num: 9, status: 'pending',
    title: 'Seasonal Models',
    titleZh: '季节性模型',
    pages: 'p375-424',
    sections: [],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch10', num: 10, status: 'pending',
    title: 'Nonlinear and Long Memory Models',
    titleZh: '非线性与长记忆模型',
    pages: 'p425-470',
    sections: [],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch11', num: 11, status: 'pending',
    title: 'Transfer Function Models',
    titleZh: '转换函数模型',
    pages: 'p471-515',
    sections: [],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch12', num: 12, status: 'pending',
    title: 'Transfer Function Model Building',
    titleZh: '转换函数模型的建立',
    pages: 'p517-564',
    sections: [],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch13', num: 13, status: 'pending',
    title: 'Intervention Analysis and Outlier Detection',
    titleZh: '干扰分析与异常值检测',
    pages: 'p565-603',
    sections: [],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch14', num: 14, status: 'pending',
    title: 'Multivariate Time Series Analysis',
    titleZh: '多元时间序列分析',
    pages: 'p605-674',
    sections: [],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch15', num: 15, status: 'pending',
    title: 'Aspects of Process Control',
    titleZh: '过程控制',
    pages: 'p675-717',
    sections: [],
  },
];

const done = chapters.filter(c => c.status === 'done').length;
const total = chapters.length;
const pct = Math.round(done / total * 100);
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <BaseHead title="Box 时间序列分析精读笔记 | Python Ship" description="Box, Jenkins & Reinsel《Time Series Analysis: Forecasting and Control》精读笔记——ARIMA、转换函数、干扰分析、多元时序、离散控制" />
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="dark" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/katex/katex.min.css" />
  <style>
    .book-container { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
    .book-hero { text-align: center; padding: 2rem 0 1rem; }
    .book-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa, #c084fc); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; margin-bottom: .3rem; }
    .book-hero .subtitle { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .book-hero .author { color: #64748b; font-size: .9rem; margin-top: .4rem; }
    .progress-section { margin: 1.2rem 0; text-align: center; }
    .progress-bar { width: 100%; height: 8px; background: #2a2d3e; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; margin: .5rem 0; }
    .progress-fill { height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #a78bfa, #c084fc); border-radius: 4px; transition: width .4s; }
    .progress-text { font-size: .85rem; color: #94a3b8; }
    .ch-card { background: #1a1d2e; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 1rem; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #2a2d3e; }
    .ch-card.done { border-left: 3px solid #4ade80; }
    .ch-card.pending { border-left: 3px solid #334155; opacity: .55; }
    .ch-header { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: .8rem 1rem; cursor: pointer; gap: .8rem; user-select: none; }
    .ch-header:hover { background: #222640; }
    .ch-num { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #a78bfa; min-width: 2.2rem; }
    .ch-info { flex: 1; }
    .ch-title-zh { font-weight: 700; color: #f1f5f9; }
    .ch-title-en { font-size: .82rem; color: #64748b; font-style: italic; }
    .ch-meta { display: flex; gap: .6rem; align-items: center; }
    .ch-pages { font-size: .78rem; color: #475569; }
    .ch-badge { font-size: .72rem; padding: .12rem .45rem; border-radius: 4px; }
    .ch-badge.done { background: #166534; color: #4ade80; }
    .ch-badge.pending { background: #1e1e2e; color: #475569; }
    .ch-toggle { font-size: .85rem; color: #64748b; transition: transform .2s; }
    .ch-card.open .ch-toggle { transform: rotate(90deg); }
    .ch-body { display: none; padding: 0 1rem 1rem; }
    .ch-card.open .ch-body { display: block; }
    .blog-link { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: .8rem; font-size: .85rem; color: #4ade80; text-decoration: none; }
    .blog-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .section { margin-bottom: .8rem; }
    .section-id { color: #a78bfa; font-weight: 700; font-size: .85rem; margin-right: .4rem; }
    .section-title { color: #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; font-size: .95rem; cursor: pointer; }
    .section-title:hover { color: #a78bfa; }
    .note { display: none; background: #13152a; border-radius: 6px; padding: .8rem 1rem; margin-top: .4rem; font-size: .88rem; color: #cbd5e1; line-height: 1.7; white-space: pre-wrap; }
    .section.open .note { display: block; }
    .back-link { display: inline-block; margin-top: 1.5rem; color: #a78bfa; text-decoration: none; font-size: .9rem; }
    .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <div class="book-container">
      <div class="book-hero">
        <h1>📈 Time Series Analysis: Forecasting and Control</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">时间序列分析：预测与控制</div>
        <div class="author">George E.P. Box, G.M. Jenkins, G.C. Reinsel · Wiley, 4th Ed. (2008) · 765p · 15 章</div>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-section">
        <div class="progress-bar">
          <div class="progress-fill" style={`width: ${pct}%`}></div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-text">{done}/{total} 章完成 ({pct}%)</div>
      </div>

      {chapters.map(ch => (
        <div class={`ch-card ${ch.status}`} id={ch.id}>
          <div class="ch-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
            <span class="ch-num">{ch.num}</span>
            <div class="ch-info">
              <div class="ch-title-zh">{ch.titleZh}</div>
              <div class="ch-title-en">{ch.title}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="ch-meta">
              {ch.pages && <span class="ch-pages">{ch.pages}</span>}
              <span class={`ch-badge ${ch.status}`}>{ch.status === 'done' ? '✅' : '⏳'}</span>
              {ch.sections.length > 0 && <span class="ch-toggle">▶</span>}
            </div>
          </div>
          {ch.sections.length > 0 && (
            <div class="ch-body">
              {ch.blogUrl && <a href={ch.blogUrl} class="blog-link">📝 感悟博客 →</a>}
              {ch.sections.map(sec => (
                <div class="section">
                  <div onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    <span class="section-id">{sec.id}</span>
                    <span class="section-title">{sec.title}</span>
                  </div>
                  {sec.note && <div class="note" set:html={sec.note.replace(/\\n/g, '<br/>')} />}
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          )}
        </div>
      ))}

      <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding: 1rem; background: #1a1d2e; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #a78bfa;">
        <a href="/blog/box-timeseries-thinking/" style="color: #a78bfa; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;">🧠 思维训练 — Box 时间序列逻辑串联 →</a>
        <div style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: .85rem; margin-top: .3rem;">推理链、跨教材知识网络、已解决的困惑</div>
      </div>

      <a href="/textbook/" class="back-link">← 返回教材目录</a>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
  <script src="/katex/katex.min.js" defer></script>
  <script src="/katex/auto-render.min.js" defer></script>
  <script is:inline>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      if (typeof renderMathInElement === 'function') {
        renderMathInElement(document.body, {
          delimiters: [
            { left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true },
            { left: '$', right: '$', display: false },
          ],
        });
      }
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
